com.aionemu.gameserver.utils.idfactory
Class IDFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.aionemu.gameserver.utils.idfactory.IDFactory

public class IDFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This class is responsible for id generation for all Aion-Emu objects.
This class is Thread-Safe.
This class is designed to be very strict with id usage. Any illegal operation will throw IDFactoryError

Author:
SoulKeeper
